Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.75,0:00:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嚮往天空 親近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.14,0:00:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翱翔於天空的神秘力量開始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.25,0:00:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏有一個傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.55,0:00:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在天之邊際雲之彼方存在著一片黃金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.72,0:00:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個故事講述了一個追尋夢想自由生存的天空盜賊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.51,0:00:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空盜團少年——酷的波瀾起伏的愛和冒險的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.49,0:02:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失散的酷和蕾\N在一個人的日子裏深深體會到彼此的重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.93,0:02:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與此同時瞄上「七煌寶樹」蕾的神秘組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.86,0:02:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ChaosChoir的攻勢愈加猛烈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.10,0:02:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於在大風車之村重逢的兩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.01,0:02:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,憑借久違的同契擊退了擬煌珠們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.00,0:02:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和希絲卡他們一起再次朝著煌珠樂園出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.00,0:02:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十六唱 追憶的子彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.41,0:03:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真壯觀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.43,0:03:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些人都是要去煌珠樂園的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.57,0:03:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.00,0:03:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.31,0:03:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然這麼隨隨便便地把「煌珠樂園」掛在嘴邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.35,0:03:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼啊 這艘船的目的地上不是存在著煌珠樂園嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.31,0:03:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的目的地是這個波魯西奧尼大陸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.65,0:03:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然傳言煌珠樂園就在這片廣袤大陸的某個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.71,0:03:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是如果我們說出\N那個詞的話就等於是通知追蹤我們的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.87,0:03:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個叫ChaosChoir的\N神秘組織何時何地來襲是不可預測的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.22,0:03:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託稍微用用腦子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.76,0:03:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老是遊玩的心態可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.30,0:03:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在守護翼也是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.76,0:04:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那 那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.78,0:04:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.58,0:04:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩是想保護蕾 她的心情...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.47,0:04:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.68,0:04:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.29,0:04:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些全部是免費的 免費的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.27,0:04:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇雅 但也不能全都吃光啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.71,0:04:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.20,0:04:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要吵架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.30,0:04:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.73,0:04:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.20,0:05:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.61,0:05:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.70,0:05:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.01,0:05:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.57,0:05:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.77,0:05:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 酷 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.89,0:05:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.39,0:05:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.81,0:05:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.30,0:05:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.81,0:05:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是遠距離狙擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.65,0:05:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人的目的很明顯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.97,0:05:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不讓酷和蕾同契 從而抓住蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.03,0:05:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.19,0:05:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 敵人就在這艘船上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.24,0:06:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊芙 你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.05,0:06:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歌聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.42,0:06:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這歌聲 好像在哪聽過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.94,0:06:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 涼爽的風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.50,0:06:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歌聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.91,0:06:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷 你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.35,0:06:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷 你已經沒事了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.02,0:06:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了 蕾在裏面 你能先照看一下嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.42,0:07:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 這氣味 是什麼來著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.58,0:07:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷 你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.66,0:07:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.00,0:07:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.84,0:07:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的氣味...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.38,0:07:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.77,0:07:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.49,0:07:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷 怎麼可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.78,0:07:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心情可以理解 可是一下子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.58,0:07:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.13,0:07:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.26,0:07:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷 果然是對蕾有不軌企圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.70,0:07:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說了不是那樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.75,0:08:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是中了那毒針造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.83,0:08:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.96,0:08:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被射中的話就會因\N事先設置在毒素中的暗號而被操縱意識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.63,0:08:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比如說 一個關鍵詞就能使其去殺沒結下仇怨的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.12,0:08:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 酷就是中了那種毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.64,0:08:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇雅 你怎麼會知道那種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.24,0:08:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是因為...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.50,0:08:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.79,0:08:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕那歌聲就是操縱酷的暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.66,0:08:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過既然已瞭解到這一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.26,0:08:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來就只剩下找出唱歌的那個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.59,0:08:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.42,0:08:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.36,0:08:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那歌聲在哪聽到過呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.48,0:08:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很想知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.37,0:08:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣一來 看上去誰都很可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.41,0:08:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.25,0:09:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這明擺著有問題的態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.70,0:09:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是說了別這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.25,0:09:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪伊娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.20,0:09:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.94,0:09:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把解毒劑交出來 瑪伊娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.18,0:09:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼 希絲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.36,0:09:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別裝傻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.84,0:09:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我唯一不及你的就是狙擊手方面的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.23,0:09:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,憑你這樣的身手 把毒射進酷體內是輕而易舉的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.91,0:09:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說唯一一項？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.50,0:09:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美貌 才能 財力 我有哪一項是不及你的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.54,0:09:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.35,0:09:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之毒什麼的我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.25,0:10:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是衝著你來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.96,0:10:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是來說我們是朋友什麼的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.98,0:10:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然不是因為友情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.49,0:10:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克魯斯輔佐官為了你現在處境很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.72,0:10:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克魯斯輔佐官他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.50,0:10:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你明擺著是為了放走七煌寶樹而申請休假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.39,0:10:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是輔佐官為你一肩承擔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.79,0:10:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.21,0:10:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想毀了輔佐官的前途嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.05,0:10:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把七煌寶樹帶回去 希絲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好考慮一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.05,0:11:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被擬煌珠完全控制了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.20,0:11:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這歌聲 讓我很不爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.25,0:11:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.27,0:11:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是ChaosChoir派來的刺客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.58,0:11:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是來抓蕾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.06,0:11:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.79,0:11:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.85,0:11:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩 躲開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.35,0:12:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍威 奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.95,0:12:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.70,0:12:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.07,0:12:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩 快去追吧 這裏交給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.83,0:12:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了 拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.68,0:12:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歌聲消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.98,0:12:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.10,0:12:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人 有人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.91,0:12:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我 不是我 不是我殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.04,0:12:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,槍 還拿著槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.33,0:12:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.54,0:12:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是守護翼的保護官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.32,0:13:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不排除危險的煌珠已混入的可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.28,0:13:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,調查工作請交給我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.44,0:13:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個 謝謝幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.57,0:13:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引起不必要的騷動很麻煩而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.14,0:13:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來是ChaosChoir的擬煌珠干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.32,0:13:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.38,0:13:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於那組織你知道些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.71,0:13:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前幾天從沙威魯多前輩那裏聽說了
