Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.86,0:13:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前不久襲擊總部的也是他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.84,0:13:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搶走在守護翼的保護館中的煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.95,0:13:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將之作為自己的部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.63,0:13:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.75,0:13:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們只把我們守護者看作同契後吸取能量的餌料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.25,0:13:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個無辜的人是被擬煌珠吸完了全部生命力後死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.79,0:13:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,分頭找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.68,0:14:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擬煌珠就在乘客之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.62,0:14:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我帶著蕾行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.20,0:14:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人的目標應該是她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.06,0:14:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的武器只有在視野好的地方纔能放開手用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.11,0:14:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍威和奇雅暫時不能戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.21,0:14:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擔心 只要打倒了敵人 酷肯定就會恢復原樣的
