Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.34,0:15:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然那個擬煌珠就是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.17,0:15:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾 快躲開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.56,0:15:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得避免傷到同契者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.87,0:15:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底發生什麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.95,0:15:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇雅 你醒了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.00,0:15:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希絲卡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.18,0:15:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了保護蕾不受到ChaosChoir的襲擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.82,0:15:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,錯了 敵人並不是ChaosChoir
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.31,0:15:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才很難對希絲卡說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.57,0:15:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我很清楚那個毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.25,0:15:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是為讓煌珠暫時老實聽話用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.22,0:15:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在守護翼中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.76,0:15:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.12,0:16:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你把毫不相關的兩個同契者都...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.29,0:16:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希絲卡 這到底是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.31,0:16:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再也受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.37,0:16:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪伊娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.81,0:16:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪伊娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.59,0:16:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希絲卡 我已經不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.35,0:16:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被擬煌珠支配了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.57,0:16:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連同我一起打倒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.94,0:16:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快動手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.40,0:16:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希絲卡 把我打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.38,0:16:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪伊娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.63,0:16:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希絲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.60,0:16:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾 快躲開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.47,0:16:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒聽見歌聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.92,0:16:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希絲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.14,0:16:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希絲卡 求你了 至少逃走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.77,0:16:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我不會逃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.64,0:17:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也沒有逃的必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.61,0:17:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼啊 這傢伙控制了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.26,0:17:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,操縱那個擬煌珠的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.85,0:17:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你吧 瑪伊娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.80,0:17:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給擬煌珠下毒 以歌聲為暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.54,0:17:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以現在聽不到歌聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.06,0:17:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為同契後的現在 你可以直接操縱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.36,0:17:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一開始打算利用那個叫酷的少年把你們都殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.03,0:17:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過偶然發現了這傢伙就稍微利用了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.80,0:17:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.80,0:17:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把七煌寶樹帶回去 同時除掉所有礙事的同契者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.06,0:17:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是給我下達的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.45,0:17:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休納貝爾的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.05,0:17:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休納貝爾這樣命令你的？
