Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.62,0:17:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休納貝爾說為了跟ChaosChoir戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.62,0:17:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,七煌寶樹是必不可少的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.21,0:18:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 把礙事的人都殺了也無所謂
